Text: when i open it up in Astro and install it, after a few seconds it says " app not installed" and quits... what am i doing wrong?

I discovered the problem

it requires  ARMv7 based cpu's, 

and the Samsung Galaxy Y has an ARMv6.

so it will never work on this phone, anyone who has this phone don't bother trying to install it. :(
works fine on my samsung galaxy exhibit 4g...
